<h1>EACL Board elections 2007-2008 </h1>

<p>
Nominations for the new EACL Board were sent out to the 
membership six weeks ago. There were no additional nominations
from the membership. We are pleased to announce that 
the officers of the European Chapter of the Association for 
Computational Linguistics 2007-2008 will be the following:
</p>
<ul>
<li>  <strong>
Chair:</strong><br>
<ul>       Alex Lascarides    (University of Edinburgh)
</ul>
<li>  <strong>Chair-elect:</strong><br>
<ul> Giorgio Satta      (University of Padua, Italy)
</ul>
<li>  <strong>Secretary:</strong><br>
<ul>   Anette Frank       (DFKI, Germany)
</ul>
<li>  <strong>Treasurer:</strong><br>
<ul>   Mike Rosner        (University of Malta)
</ul>
<li>  <strong>Advisory Board members:</strong><br>
<ul>
             Eric Gaussier      (Joseph Fourier University, Grenoble, France)<br>
             Paola Merlo        (University of Geneva, Switzerland)<br>
             Kiril Simov        (Bulgarian Academy of Sciences, Sofia, Bulgaria)<br>
             Josef van Genabith (Dublin City University, Ireland)<br>
</ul>

<li><strong>Nominating committee:</strong><br>
<ul>
             John Carroll       (University of Sussex, UK)<br>
             Claire Gardent     (LORIA, Nancy, France)<br>
             Gertjan van Noord  (University of Groningen, Netherlands)<br>
             Felisa Verdejo     (Universidad Nacional de Educacion a Distancia, Spain)<br>
</ul>
<p>The EACL Student Board remains unchanged:</p>
<ul>
             Nuria Bertomeu (Saarland University, Germany)<br>
             Jonathon Read (University of Sussex, United Kingdom)<br>
             Violeta Seretan (University of Geneva, Switzerland)<br>
</ul>
<p>We thank the outgoing members of the previous EACL board 
for their years of excellent service to the CL community:</p>
<ul>
Gertjan van Noord   (Chair)<br>
Galia Angelova      (Executive Board)<br>
Ido Dagan           (Executive Board)<br>
